Product description

Refined rice bran oil is a relatively new entrant in the cooking oil segment and is considered to be the healthiest option available at present. Refined rice bran oil features mufa and pufa in an almost equal ratio, which is considered to be ideal for any oil. The oil also has a high smoke point which makes it perfect for deep frying food. Its golden colour and neutral taste ensure that food cooked retains its natural taste and flavour.

How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.
